description: Try our easy to follow Spaghetti Bolognese with mushrooms recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Spaghetti Bolognese with mushrooms Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g San Remo spaghetti pasta no 5
500 g Dolmio traditional recipe tomato & basil pasta sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Add tomato basil pasta sauce then reduce heat, cover and simmer for 10 minutes. Serve with pasta, topped with grated parmesan cheese.
